{"tid":1099950,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"岩岩上堂唔小心放左個屁  賴左屎","createTime":"2019-04-10T06:14:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-10T07:22:46.000Z","uid":1734,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"20d23ba82d7fcc3b3ae7b6d38e802832f5715270","tid":1099950,"uid":1734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T06:14:49.000Z","msg":"話說岩岩lunch 食左個潭仔十小 辣到仆街 到上中文堂個肚勁痛 但唔敢同老師講去廁所<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 驚比同學笑我柯屎  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁我死忍難忍 都頂到縮返入去 但過多左陣又痛返 今次頂唔順 放左個濕屁 但唔響 無人聽到 不過臭到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 隔離左右都出聲話臭 我當然扮唔係我 話好臭頂唔住去廁所避避 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n去到廁所一除褲 成條低褲都係屎 仲要濕濕地  好似福建炒飯咁 我唯有成條除左佢 掉左落下一層男廁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以家無著低褲上堂"},{"pid":"c2e14714c852ea5c812aee64d50b49464b6d2ec6","tid":1099950,"uid":149383,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T06:17:09.000Z","msg":"啱晒啦 呢幾日咁熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n比弟弟放鬆下都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd0dbb26c8c5a9d696d80ea69f02d3ef2ccea5de","tid":1099950,"uid":29080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T06:17:59.000Z","msg":"牙蓋都試過癩屎"},{"pid":"919922d2209ac9d107a0227fbff3ba0e74b69757","tid":1099950,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cd0dbb26c8c5a9d696d80ea69f02d3ef2ccea5de","tid":1099950,"uid":29080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T06:17:59.000Z","msg":"牙蓋都試過癩屎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T06:18:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/as